                                                    <div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"></p><p>Kliiniline patoloogia II kursus koosneb 3 moodulist: n<span style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">aistehaiguste patoloogia, d</span><span style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">ermatopatoloogia ja rinnapatoloogia</span><span style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">.</span></p><div></div><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><span style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">Aktiivõppel põhinev kursus nõuab eelnevat kodust ettevalmistust. Enne seminari tutvu õppematerjalidega ja soorita lühike enesekontrollitest. Igas testis on 5 juhuslikku küsimust ja teste saab sooritada piiramatu arv kordi 5 minuti jooksul pärast testi avamist. Püüa sooritada testid 100% tulemusele.</span><br></p><hr id="null"><p>The course consists of 3 modules:&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">Gynecological Pathology,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">Dermatopathology, and Breast Pathology</span><span style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">.</span></p><p>Active learning based course requires prior preparation at home. Before the seminar,&nbsp;<span lang="EN">familiarize yourself with the learning materials and take a short self-test.&nbsp;Each test has 5 random questions, and the tests can be taken an unlimited number of times within 5 minutes of opening the test. Try to complete the tests for 100% result.</span></p></div>
