                                                    <div class="no-overflow"><p></p><ul><li><span style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">Praktikumides/seminarides osalemine on kohustuslik.&nbsp;Ühes praktikumis/seminaril osalemine annab kuni 10 punkti, maksimaalne kogutud punktide summa on 40, lävend on 35 punkti.&nbsp;</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">Kontrolltöö-arvestus (</span><span class="" style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">elektrooniline</span><span class="" style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: rgb(255, 51, 102); --darkreader-inline-color: var(--darkreader-text-ff3366, #ff1d56);" data-darkreader-inline-color=""> </span><span style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">test). Kontrolltöö-arvestusele saamiseks peab olema kursuse jooksul seminarides osalemise eest kogutud vähemalt 35 punkti. Igal rühmal toimub
arvestus kindlal kokkulepitud päeval ja kellaajal. </span><strong>Rühmad x ja x</strong>&nbsp;saavad testi sooritada <strong>x</strong><strong>&nbsp;kell x-x</strong>&nbsp;Biomeedikumis (<strong>ruumis 1030</strong>) 1 kord 40 minuti jooksul. Testis on 18 valikvastustega küsimust, igaüks eraldi lehel. Lehtede vahel on võimalik vabalt liikuda. Järgmisele või eelmisele lehele liikudes sisestatud vastus salvestatakse. Salvestatud vastust saate muuta kuni testi lõpetamiseni. Enne 40 minuti möödumist ja testi sulgumist peate jõudma vajutada nuppu "<em style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">Esita kõik ja lõpeta</em><span style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">" testi viimasel lehel all servas. Hindamine on 100-pallilisel skaalal. Lävend on 70% maksimaalsest.&nbsp;</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">Kursus on arvestatud, kui kursuse jooksul on praktikumides/seminarides kogutud vähemalt 35 punkti ja kursuse lõpus kontrolltöö-arvestus on sooritatud vähemalt 70% lävendile.</span></li></ul><p></p><hr id="null"><ul><li>All practicums/seminars are compulsory.&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">Participation in one practicum/seminar gives up to 10 points, the maximum amount of points collected is 40, and the threshold is 35 points.<br></span></li><li>Final test -&nbsp;pass/fail evaluation.&nbsp;The minimum test score is 70% of the maximum.&nbsp;To qualify for the final test, at least 35 points must be
collected for participation in seminars during the course. Groups <strong>X</strong> can take the test on <strong>X</strong> from <strong>X-X</strong> at the Biomedical Center (<strong>room 1030</strong>) once in 40 minutes. The test has 18 multiple-choice questions, each on a separate page. It is possible to move freely between pages. The entered answer is saved when moving to the next or previous page. You can change the saved answer until you submit the test. Before the 40 minutes are up and the test closes, you must be able to press the "<em>Submit all and finish</em>" button on the bottom edge of the last page of the test. Evaluation is on a 100-point scale. The threshold is 70% of the maximum.</li><li>To obtain&nbsp;positive result, at least 35 points must be collected
during the course, and the percentage of correct answers on the final test must
not be less than 70% of the maximum.</li></ul></div>
